OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F166A1773205685
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloudy morning, with some
OL,6,Fparts dry, but also outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fpossible. Occasionally heavy and
OL,8,Fblustery rain then moves southeast
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon, clearing North
OL,10,FYorkshire into the evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold and
OL,13,Fbreezy Friday with brighter spell and
OL,14,Foccasional showers, wintry over hills.
OL,15,FLess cold Saturday, but still the odd
OL,16,Fshower likely. Further rain and strong
OL,17,Fwinds spreading east Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
